data.text: @JayneBYoung @Lewisno1fan Pursued Harry? Who are you kidding? The guy said it himself. He had to convince her to go to Botswana with him for their 3rd date. Everybody who knows him he fell crazy in love. When she asked the matchmaker lady if he was nice it's because she didn't want to play around.
@Lewisno1fan It's like @FoxNews here in the US but multiplied by 10.
